Touch him.

2354
02:34:51,041 --> 02:34:52,042
Say it.

2355
02:34:54,919 --> 02:34:56,879
Say his fucking name, Ruth!

2356
02:34:58,840 --> 02:34:59,841
Say it.

2357
02:35:03,345 --> 02:35:05,513
